        <h3>Our Approach</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Sticking close to the essentials of what makes MVC.<br />
                This keeps &quot;XSpy&quot; close to common standards like SQL and HTML5<br />
                &nbsp;
            </li>
            <li>
                Shopping Cart with row by row database updates via AJAX<br />
                &nbsp;
            </li>
            <li>
                Database table &quot;OrderDetails&quot; gains column "LineNumbers".&nbsp;<br />
                Added to reflect our experience of programming for Shipping and Warehousing systems<br />
                where Item Line Numbers are a common point of reference for workers.<br />
                &nbsp;
